    "created_at": "2016-04-28T15:13:57Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-04-28T15:13:57Z",
    "body": "Looks like the problem is that the ID is not persistent, the monitor is not found in the vector.\n\n```\nvoid Screen::OnDisplayRemoved(const gfx::Display& old_display) {\n  auto iter = FindById(&displays_, old_display.id());\n  if (iter == displays_.end())\n    return;\n\n  displays_.erase(iter);\n  Emit(\"display-removed\", old_display);\n}\n```\n"
  },
